Sample Time: Data Courtesy of California Department of Fish and Wildlife.
Data column availability is linked to species, adipose fin clip status, and water year.
Fish with forklength >300mm excluded from results.
'Loss', 'LAD Loss' and 'CWT Loss' are calculated by SacPAS.
Citation: Columbia Basin Research, University of Washington. (2022). SacPAS Loss and Salvage Detail. Available from www.cbr.washington.edu/sacramento/data/query_loss_detail.html.
